      "alt": "Adam Selipsky in • 2nd\nCEO of Helix Digital Infrastructure. For...\nVisit my website 3h •\nG\n+ Follow\nIn my 15 years helping build a $100B revenue business and scale cloud infrastructure with Amazon Web Services (AWS), I saw firsthand what happens when demand for compute outpaces the physical infrastructure behind it.\nData centers, power, and connectivity have all too often been built on separate tracks. In the unprecedented infrastructure build-out of the Al era, that fragmentation has become an industry-wide bottleneck. This is slowing down the benefits of Al for enterprises, startups, governments, non-profits, and citizens worldwide.\nThat's why I'm excited to work with KKR to launch and take on the role of CEO at Helix Digital Infrastructure.\nHelix brings a new approach to infrastructure delivery, integrating data centers, power, and connectivity to help hyperscalers meet accelerating Al demand with greater speed, scale, and certainty.\nSupported by KKR's leading infrastructure platform and launched with founding partners Kuwait Investment Authority, NVIDIA and Vistra Corp., Helix will operate as a new company that combines the assets, capital, and hands-on technology expertise needed to accelerate Al infrastructure deployment.",
